"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The set_style() function is being used with the rc argument, which is not the intended use according to the seaborn documentation. The rc parameter should only be used with set_context() or set_theme(). Instead, set_style() should be called with a style name or a dictionary of parameters that are part of the style definition.\", \"patch\": \"14c14\\n< sns.set_style(rc=style_dict)\\n---\\n> sns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n\"}"